-- Colombian Unions to Strike Over Wage Increase, Colombiano Says
-- B y   P a b l o   G o n z a l e z
-- 2012-12-29T17:49:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-29/colombian-unions-to-strike-over-wage-increase-colombiano-says.html
Colombian unions will hold a strike
to protest the 4 percent minimum wage increase given by the
government yesterday, El Colombiano reported today, citing union
leader Domingo Tovar.  The strike will take place during the first quarter of
2013, the Medellin-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Pablo Gonzalez in Buenos Aires at 
 pgonzalez49@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
